  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hot and cold buffet breakfast</p>
<p>Five course evening meal with choice of three main dishes plus salad buffet, cheese and fruit selection</p>
<p>Weekly gala dinner and buffet evening</p>
<p>Special Christmas celebration with a visit from Father Christmas and carol singing</p>
