  <description><![CDATA[<p>This superb, family-run hotel offers an excellent quality of both food and accommodation and has a loyal following of Inghams guests.</p>
<h2>Top quality service</h2>
<p>The Köll-Scheiber family pride themselves on their high standards and attention to detail. Enjoy the magnificent views from the lounge and bar and an excellent five course dinner in the restaurant.</p>
<h2>Ski-in, Ski-out</h2>
<p>The Hotel Gotthard is located next to the Hohe Mut lift and you will have ski-in, ski-out access to the slopes. The centre of Obergurgl is a short five minute walk away.</p>
<h2>Wellness</h2>
<p>Take in incredible view over the mountains in the hotel's outdoor panoramic whirlpool. The large wellness area also has an indoor pool, Roman sweat bath, sauna, salt steam bath, herb steam bath and ice fountain. </p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Gotthard the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
