  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Austrian twin </strong>rooms are around 36m² and spacious enough to sleep up to four using the double sofa bed in the lounge area. These rooms have a bath and west facing balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Cat. B Junior Suites </strong>offer the most space at around 42m². These rooms can also sleep up to four and have south facing balconies.</p>
<p><strong>Single </strong>rooms with bath or shower are available on request so please call us to book these.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
